data.description: Welcome home to 8940 Woodcreek Circle--a charming four-bedroom, three-and-a-half-bath brick home overlooking the 14th green of Porters Neck Country Club with stunning views of Lake Nona. Upon entering the double doors your eyes will be drawn to the expansive water and golf views as you settle into the two-story living room complete with built-ins around the fireplace. Moving around the corner leads you to a butler's pantry and then into the gourmet chef's kitchen complete with top-of-the-line appliances including the centerpiece Wolf 6-burner gas range, double ovens with convection, Sub-Zero refrigerator and Miele dishwasher anchored by an oversized island with granite tops. The kitchen and additional sitting area both have spectacular golf course views. Step out onto your private screened porch to unwind after a long day and enjoy the sunset. The first-level master suite is complete with a walk-in closet, walk-in shower, and jetted tub. Finishing off the first level is a formal dining room, powder room, and expansive laundry room. Upstairs boasts three bedrooms and two bathrooms and a large walk-in attic space for easy storage. The fourth bedroom with en suite bath also has a private balcony with arguably the best vantage point for water views.A few upgrades to this impressive home include a NEW ROOF OCT 2023, new Bosch 500 dishwasher, plantation shutters and customized shades throughout the house, shared well for irrigation, encapsulated crawl space, central vacuum, and hurricane shutters.Residents of Porters Neck Plantation enjoy access to the Intracoastal Waterway via the community boat ramp which also has a picnic area. Memberships to the top-rated Porters Neck Country Club are available. Amenities include golf, fitness, dining, pool, tennis, and pickleball.
